Cell["\<\
Mean per-round payoff, row strategy against column strategy (\[Epsilon]=0). \
Warm = high. The cooperative cluster (top-left block) sustains mutual R=3; \
AllD and the extortioner do well in single matchups but drag the whole field \
down.\
\>", "Text",
 CellMargins->{{70, 70}, {2, 14}},
 FontSize->11,
 FontSlant->Italic,
 FontColor->GrayLevel[
  0.35],ExpressionUUID->"01198836-8567-4700-874a-1293b0af771d"],

