Cell["\<\
Moran process, long-run composition vs noise. Finite-population stochasticity \
makes the picture grainier, but the qualitative story survives: forgiving \
cooperators at low-to-moderate noise, defection-dominated outcomes as noise \
grows.\
\>", "Text",
 CellMargins->{{70, 70}, {2, 14}},
 FontSize->11,
 FontSlant->Italic,
 FontColor->GrayLevel[
  0.35],ExpressionUUID->"ca44c78f-ccfe-4023-a2df-7c098fb4a6a9"],

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["Takeaway. ",
  FontWeight->Bold],
 "\"Which strategy is evolutionarily stable?\" has ",
 StyleBox["no noise-independent answer",
  FontSlant->Italic],
 ". The same population that converges on generous reciprocity in a clean \
channel converges on pure defection in a noisy one."
}], "Text",
 CellMargins->{{50, 50}, {6, 
  6}},ExpressionUUID->"183f653f-9d20-453e-85bd-72b7dbc7915a"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["4. Discovering strategies that beat Tit-for-Tat under noise", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"3180d0f2-86f8-4166-96ea-1484e08954e4"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Can we do better than the textbook strategies? In the spirit of an \
automated-research loop \[Dash] ",
 StyleBox["propose \[Rule] evaluate \[Rule] accept \[Rule] repeat",
  FontSlant->Italic],
 " \[Dash] we search the memory-one space ",
 StyleBox["\[Theta] = (open, pCC, pCD, pDC, pDD) \[Element] [0,1]^5",
  FontFamily->"Times",
  FontSlant->Italic],
 " for the best response to the standard field at each noise level. A greedy \
hill-climb gives the narrative; a small genetic algorithm is the workhorse."
}], "Text",
 CellMargins->{{50, 50}, {6, 
  6}},ExpressionUUID->"33e3a084-2569-408d-8a41-9f1a8a7a6ce7"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
fitness[theta_, eps_] := Mean[
   meanMatch[memOne[theta[[1]], theta[[2;;]]], #, rounds, eps, reps][[1]] & \
/@ field];

(* greedy accept/reject loop -- the autoresearch analogy *)
champion = {1, 1, 0, 1, 0};                       (* start from Tit-for-Tat \
*)
Do[ proposal = clip[champion + RandomVariate[NormalDistribution[0, .12], 5]];
    If[fitness[proposal, eps] > fitness[champion, eps], champion = proposal],
  {150}]\
\>", "Input",
 CellMargins->{{60, 30}, {6, 6}},
 FontSize->11,ExpressionUUID->"87163e61-66ec-4aca-9e00-48306be132ef"],

